My Artwork at Art Basel Miami🎨💃🏻🙏🏽✨it’s been a wild ride and I am beyond grateful for the experience to be featured as an Artist at Art Basel this year. Thank you for the support and our team who made it possible for me to show and share my Art and spread its vibration 🤍 
Be inspiring and be inspired. Absorb, reflect, create and express. Support other artists and expand your horizons, always. 
Forever grateful 💃🏻❤️🙏🏽
